race.description: Sky Racing Qtis Three-Year-Old Maiden Handicap
race.comment: YOU SEXY THING (4) had been knocking on the door in Sydney before his 1.4L defeat in a rich Magic Millions Maiden at the Gold Coast. Has an awkward gate but Maloney is a key jockey booking and she should have this field well covered. KATIE AINE (14) is an improver in the Munce yard. She began awkwardly when well supported at Eagle Farm her latest. ASTERN EFFORT (17) brings close-up placings from Eagle Wareick and Eagle Farm last time. He's improving and from an inside gate can make top three. TURBO TORQUE (7) is third-up with a lot more in the tank. Maps well and Wiggins stays aboard. Goes in at a price.
